@Beephe, ashn2k, and anyone experiencing crashes every time:

This is due to an issue with duplicate fonts.  To fix this:
1.  Open Font Book
2.  Select all fonts (? + A)
3.  Option/Right Click the fonts
4.  Select "Resolve Duplicates"
5.  Done!!!

This worked immediately for me and now i am enjoying the 'new' equation editor that was not on mac office before now...
